Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}常に魔力を制限しているのに?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.08,0:21:15.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}那是历经磨炼得到的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:15.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}それは血のにじむような努力の賜物に見えますが
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.55,0:21:19.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}何况你付诸了一生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:19.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}それこそ人生を懸けたような
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}気が付いていたの?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}我们都一起旅行多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}何年一緒に旅をしていると思っているんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}我的故事很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.52,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}面白い話じゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}構いませんよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}这也是为了后来者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}それに後学のためにもなります
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.61,0:21:34.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:34.23,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&69808C\4c&69808C}{\bord2}何で
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}もしかしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.32,0:21:39.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}我的孩子将来会成为魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:39.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}{\c&CCCCCC}私の子供は魔法使いになるかもしれませんよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\bord2.5}僧侣不是不结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\bord2.5}僧侶は生涯独身でしょ?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.37,0:21:54.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&404040\4c&404040}{\bord2}为什么侍奉女神的人都是怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:54.75,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&404040\4c&404040}{\bord2}何で女神様に仕える連中は変なヤツが多いんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&555152\4c&555152}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}请容我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.25,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&555152\4c&555152}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}遠慮しておくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&555152\4c&555152}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}已经有人夸奖过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&555152\4c&555152}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}もう別のヤツに褒めてもらったから
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E7073\4c&6E7073}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E7073\4c&6E7073}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E7073\4c&6E7073}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}你有个好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E7073\4c&6E7073}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}いい友人を持ったな
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.72,0:22:06.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E7073\4c&6E7073}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}芙莉莲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:06.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E7073\4c&6E7073}{\bord2}{\c&EDF3F5}フリーレン
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.89,0:22:08.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&EDF3F5}请好好珍惜他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:08.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&EDF3F5}大事にしろ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&EDF3F5}不，他已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&EDF3F5}いや、その人はもう…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.61,0:22:19.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&EDF3F5}他如今在天国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:19.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&EDF3F5}今は天国にいるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\c&ECEDE4}那你们早晚会相见的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\c&ECEDE4}なら、いずれ会えるな
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\c&ECEDE4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\c&ECEDE4}そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}{\bord2}{\c&C0C3C4}我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}{\bord2}{\c&C0C3C4}俺はこっちだ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.70,0:22:30.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\bord2}芙莉莲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:30.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\bord2}フリーレン
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.20,0:22:33.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}这不是最后一别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:33.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}今生の別れとは思わん
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.54,0:22:35.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}数百年后再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:35.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&262626\4c&262626}{\bord2}何百年後かに、またな
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.46,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}大叔也要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.46,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}おっさんも元気でな
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.46,0:22:42.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}很高兴遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:42.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}楽しかったぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.88,0:22:47.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&425B6E\4c&425B6E}{\bord2}谢谢你送的吊坠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:47.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&425B6E\4c&425B6E}{\bord2}ペンダント、ありがとうございました
